sanam teri kasam is a 1982 hindi-language indian feature film directed by narendra bedi and produced by reena roy 's sister , barkha roy , starring kamal haasan , reena roy , kader khan and ranjeet . the film became a " semi-hit " at the box office and was more successful in the big cities . r.d. burman won his first filmfare best music director award for sanam teri kasam .